events.text: I knew he had it in him! Like Euler, Descartes, Gauss… my boy’s going to be one of the greats! I can’t wait to show him the more complex material, he’ll love it! Thank goodness for the library, I suppose we’ll start at algebra…
...oh! And then we’ll move onto applications of Maxwell’s equations…
The father continues to mutter to himself, planning out a curriculum.
